title: [Rumor Woods]
description: Golden light and shadows dance across the high grasses of the small clearing where multiple trails scatter in various directions.  Twisting its way through the aspen roots and tumbling mounds of vegetation, a burbling brook bubbles up from beneath the damp ground and cuts a singular path to the southwest before disappearing again.  A conical tent of sky blue silk emblazoned with a silver ram sits in a flat section of ground that is free of mud and snow.
